  <brief_title>Predictive Factors for the Development of Osteonecrosis After the Treatment of the Developmental Dislocated Hip</brief_title>
  <official_title>Predictive Factors for the Development of Osteonecrosis After the Treatment of the Developmental Dislocated Hip. A Comparison of Early Open Reduction Versus Late Open Reduction With Combined Pemberton and Femoral Osteotomies</official_title>
  <sponsors>
